  <summary date="2023-08-09T18:41:19Z" status="Introduced in House">IT Service Corps Act

This bill includes programs dedicated to the achievement of digital equity in underserved communities, including through supporting digital inclusion activities and enhancing digital literacy among individuals in such communities, within federally supported national service programs (e.g., AmeriCorps).</summary>
